Interface ChangeRecordSelectable

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface ChangeRecordSelectable
extends EntitySelectable<ChangeRecord>
    Interface to enable OData entity selectors for ChangeRecord. This interface is used by ChangeRecordField and ChangeRecordLink.

    Available instances:

    • CHG_RECORD_APPLICATION

    • CHANGE_RECORD
    • CHANGE_RECORD_TYPE
    • PARENT_CHANGE_RECORD_UUID
